  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\nOften when signing transactions especially from Dapp in emulators, network fee can take forever to be fetched and calculated which results in 0 as network fee TX value. \r\nIt's not always reproducible (that network fee takes more than 1 min to update) but happens often when e2e tests are running: e.g. https://app.saucelabs.com/tests/02ffaf2d675747efb0733450b8251b04?auth=7d0aecd1dbc9e8dfb11316c079d89064#103 (from 3:29 - 4:29 - network fee 0 and so 'Sing with password' disabled)\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nNetwork fee updated in less than 3 seconds after 'Sending TX' bottom-sheet appears\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nNetwork fee update value 1 minute after 'Sending TX' bottom-sheet appears\r\n\r\n<img width=\"409\" alt=\"Screenshot 2019-10-15 at 19 25 39\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/66850514-a46df500-ef81-11e9-91bd-b1545d2c67d7.png\">\r\n\r\n#### Notes\r\n\r\nNot related to any recent PRs, it was happening in the past. \r\n#### Acceptance Criteria\r\nWhen `Sending [token]` transaction bottom-sheet appears, Network Fee update it's values in less than 3 seconds\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status and create new account \r\n- Navigate to DApps -> enter simpledapp.eth in URL and submit\r\n- Navigate to Assets tab \r\n- Tap 'Request STT' button and verify transaction fee is not 0 \r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n- Status version: develop nightly `0.14.0 2019151002`\r\n- Operating System: Android and iOS \r\n\r\n\r\n",
